  ## Side knowledge store.

  By progressing as your main path, you gradually unlock more side knowledge to purchase.
  At the beginning you get access to tier 1 side knowledge and you can also select one of 3 random tier 1 side knowledge for free.
  Tier 1 and 2 side knowledge cost 1 point, and tier 3 cost 2 points.
  By collecting influences using codex you can get more side knowledge for free or at a discount.

